Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星运输船遭不明物体袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20名船员去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军紧急应对总部认为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次事件系UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即未知敌人的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事件仍在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自UE发动的第一起袭击事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天使陨落之日」后14年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦政府至今宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法探明敌人的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市民的不满日益高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来了吗 菲利特 菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 又熬夜了对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两眼通红
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午开始的启动实验 通知你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然！司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个普通孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的才能让所有人都惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 高达马上就能站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么急…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 没伤着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 原来是菲利特和艾米莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…不是高达的手臂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么装在那上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看好不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到运动性太棒了 不舍得拆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要试用高达部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得事先通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 高达是司令专门委托给菲利特的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 迟到了 菲利特 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 要迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再自作主张了 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特真是 提起高达就激动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷 您请看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是明日野家族世代相传的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的战士 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 在过往的大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被称作是为世界带来和平的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些战士们 过去也被叫做机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 巨大的人形兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中的众多名机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都出自代代经营机动战士制造业的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明日野家族 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要制造出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的救世主 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了吗 外星人又惹事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是UE吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来历不明 不是外星人是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人们都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 只要住在诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和我们没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们就没怎么来过人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我们开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先从…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师怎么看昨天的事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,货船疑似被UE袭击的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 是不是也该想好应对措施？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座诺拉也不是绝对安全的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特的被害妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有危险的话 会发布警告的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到现在为止从来没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的袭击 有一定规律性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据规律解开方程式…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 答案表明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次遭袭的就是诺拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有完没完！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什么 菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看你现在成绩优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦松懈马上就会落后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为去掺和军方那个什么机动战士开发计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会满脑子这些不切实际的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当初就反对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到座位上去 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被退学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 挨骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 挨骂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人说不定已经在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离上次来天文馆 有多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉会被袭击的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座卫星上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只把那些看成是发生在遥远世界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为谁都没有被UE袭击过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我亲眼看见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故乡奥凡在UE的袭击中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个城市瞬间化作火海的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们根本杀人不眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈临死前 给我的记忆体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈说 这里面有我该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面记录有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士的设计图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前家里画像上一模一样的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是提到的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画中的救世主 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那台白色战士的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈一定想说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我制造机动战士去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗中 拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以菲利特造的机动战士也叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是救世主的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 城市里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那闪光是…爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是它们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是UE！这样下去城市就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是UE…他们真的来了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人确认为UE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防卫队请出战！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士是什么情况 出动如此缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外的杰诺亚斯直接前往迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三号机库 德列斯小队能否出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去出口会被控制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克 古鲁迪克副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥防守第四到第八防区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉你不用来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52}全员战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52\fad(0,400)}重复 全员战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是外星人 该怎么打？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 艾米莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杰诺亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 想急死我这个老头子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是UE的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是什么机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们只会到处破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台搬运车上 运的是高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赶忙把它藏到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的杰诺亚斯被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯 出动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达可以战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 高达还动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离实战差远了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测试时站起来走了两步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样足以确认运动性了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个 拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对第一次驾驶的人来说风险太大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用杰诺亚斯出战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 这里也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去里面避难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是驾驶员 怎么可能开得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我造的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体的情况 我最了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是了解就能打赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉甘·德列斯 杰诺亚斯出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请赶紧打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,14年来从没被人击败过的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,营救驾驶员 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准去！你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 抬他出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 什么都没做成…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 大家都会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人就是那样残暴 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只有战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平衡器只能边驾驶边调节了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是想让菲利特开它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特的觉悟是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不输给大兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用妈妈给我的这台高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和它们战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来启动顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我升起托架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不想让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…一直看在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特有多么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特的战斗就永远不会结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量系统 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE系统 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 高达好像要出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员是拉甘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎先生 这是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 一定要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去救出大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野 高达出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型机准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四机库防爆舱门确认开启
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们见识见识你传说中的力量 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为大家 也为你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为救世主 与高达一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一台 就这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 有什么武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用 那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗 UE的机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有增援 想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 这就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来 还不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特果然是个了不起的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙什么时候变得这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们胜利了 史上首次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这种程度的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会改变任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以成为反击的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在好好享受这份胜利…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才的机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是来自卫星外部的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使陨落之日 又要重演…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.37,0:22:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
